{"tid":1460722,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[812 和你飛] 重返機場","createTime":"2019-08-13T04:32:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:53:08.000Z","uid":31003,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ba03b856e29b1a9b16ac875de3e61a94c2ea7318","tid":1460722,"uid":31003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:32:35.000Z","msg":"8月12號 , 我去左機場兩次, 我想講關於第二次去既經歷,<br />\n<br />\n第一次, 我廢, 我冇用, 我淆底, 6點鐘我同女朋友跟大隊走左。<br />\n<br />\n第二次, 首先講講個原因, 就係我回家途中, 我地發現依然有唔少人留左係度,<br />\n<strong>我地先醒覺到, 點解我地既憤怒咁脆弱, 811 換黎既野班黑警只要郁下條尾就可以驅散左。</strong><br />\n<strong>大家下一次要聚集咁多人, 又需要幾多人既犧牲去換番黎, 覺得自己好自私點解會捨得掉低機場班爸絲??  </strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">因此, 我地重返機場。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我地抵達時間約 9 點30分, 買左少少物資入去打算贖罪,<br />\n當時有一個戴眼鏡戴住頭盔既男仔, 主動埋黎問我要唔要幫手,<br />\n我地婉拒左, 但佢亦都指示左大約邊度需要熱食同飲品等等。<br />\n<br />\nT1 去T2, T2番T1, 來來回回兜轉左幾個圈, 當中有好多特別事, 想再聽可以再分享,<br />\n而家我想講番果個男仔, 接近尾聲我番到去T1 離境大堂機鐵站位置, 當時好多物資集中緊,<br />\n好多熱食未派曬, 根住我就盡力派埋剩低既熱食, 派唔曬D食物就會變&quot;林鄭&quot;。<br />\n<br />\n果陣我地撞番果個男仔, 我話幫幫手拎D 熱食啦, 我就走架喇, 派唔曬就要掉......<br />\n跟住個男仔主動話, 咁你交架車仔俾我啦, 我幫你派啦!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我話咁有義氣我幫你手陪你行個圈。<br />\n行完A 區派熱食時間差不多12點15分AM ,我期間同佢傾左陣計 :<br />\n<br />\n個男仔應該仲讀緊書, 好有禮貌, <br />\n當時 D 麥記包呀飲品都散得7788, 熱食派剩兩盒飯<br />\n飲品佢拎左支寶礦力, 我拎埋剩低果D。<br />\n<br />\n男仔: 算啦, 我拎埋果兩盒飯佢啦, 反正我好耐都冇食過飯。<br />\n(我諗佢意思係指佢成日出黎發夢, 冇乜點食到飯呢類野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n我: 太好喇... 派曬呢度喇...D 豉油(廿幾包) 我拎番去啦...打邊爐之應該用到)<br />\n男仔: 今日辛苦你地喇, 請問機場尾班幾點<br />\n我: 我都唔清楚, 我地渣車過黎, 你住邊區?<br />\n男仔: 我住 XXX 架, <br />\n我: 下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我住大西北... errrrr.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男仔即時講: 唔洗理我架喇, 我可以係度訓<br />\n(當時我以為佢主要係想留守)<br />\n我: 咁你一定要小心D 呀, 保持警覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n男仔: 機鐵太貴啦, 7-80 蚊一程, 我情願係度訓一晚, 留番D錢去<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">買</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">豬</span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咀</span></span><br />\n個心已經有D拿住拿住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男仔: 我D豬咀同餅全部都要換喇, 呢D野好貴<br />\n我話: 我冇豬咀係身...你要唔要現金呀?? (下午散水果陣我掉曬GEAR 係屋企...好想幫手唯有咁問)<br />\n男仔: 梗係唔洗啦, 我已經買左架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個時候番到去機鐵站出口了,<br />\n男仔見到有鐵到左, 行緊途中佢CHECK 左12點9左右先係尾班,<br />\n當時有架鐵到站,<br />\n男仔: 我都係坐機鐵走喇廢事坐尾班, 番去換件衫休息一下, 聽日我地再見啦!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(我猶豫左, 冇出聲面有難色, 因為我連續出左4日... 星期日同星期一兩日只訓左一個鐘唔夠, 打算星期二抖抖。)<br />\n男仔跑往機鐵趕車, 表情有D失落亦同時體諒:『我地有機會再見啦, byebye』<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住我地就咁同佢講聲辛苦曬之類, 番左屋企, 訓醒又再次後悔, 冇車佢番去, 冇答應到佢聽日見,<br />\n如果你係爸打, 我想同你講聲,<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>好呀, 我地813 再見啦!!!!!</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我知你地睇到呢度一定想屌到我開花, 我自己都係咁鬧自己<br />\n麻煩大家幫手推POST 俾其他人見到!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>813 機場見!!!!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"87abe27a4c0e15d6a61c5b836ec7390097711343","tid":1460722,"uid":14262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:32:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">寧可輸給極權 絕不自我放棄！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n一日場仗未打完，都唔可以認命！<br />\n所有想自殺想放棄既人聽住，同我地堅持下去！<br />\n依家未係心灰既時候，<br />\n如果場革命係因為放棄而輸<br />\n仲點對得住過世義士及被捕義士！<br />\n仲邊有面目做人！<br />\n同我地打埋場仗佢！<br />\n<br />\n<em>（幫推及傳遞訊息，一個手足不能少）</em>"},{"pid":"23dd8350c27e07148fa136b6d22400306d0b210d","tid":1460722,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:33:25.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"8b62c6a9f7bee5db6e01357005a06308b6dbdf62","tid":1460722,"uid":251773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:37:53.000Z","msg":"今日繼續和你飛"},{"pid":"2fee92778455dc1535deabef547b8ece8b408871","tid":1460722,"uid":31003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:39:39.000Z","msg":"813 機場!!!<br />\n繼續和你飛!! 今日我地一齊派啦!!!<br />\n如果你睇到!<br />\n想同你講聲對唔住呀沉日冇覆你!!!"},{"pid":"428a641d4ff8300f27ca8d33c1e8a177827ba559","tid":1460722,"uid":31003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:42:17.000Z","msg":"希望你見到,<br />\n即使呢刻見唔到, 亦希望一陣我地見番!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">813 機場見!</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5bda6344bd5f34a3a7778897e7dbb31318c30379","tid":1460722,"uid":31003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b62c6a9f7bee5db6e01357005a06308b6dbdf62","tid":1460722,"uid":251773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:37:53.000Z","msg":"今日繼續和你飛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:44:10.000Z","msg":"我會拎番沉日果堆紙皮文宣架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa923fb4382d22276451c849a17d9de60543ab59","tid":1460722,"uid":31003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:45:48.000Z","msg":"利申: 非gay <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4123a32c3f9a444517356fd15e029c79a2ea26ef","tid":1460722,"uid":74958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:46:25.000Z","msg":"612<br />\n721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"8392c40abcbefa1e7f3587c084cf00114b7e6af8","tid":1460722,"uid":31003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:48:06.000Z","msg":"BTW 收工先過去, 會拎物資入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我罷左幾日, 容許我做一陣社畜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc4409015b1465e82d522bdc2d68cb9025999a2","tid":1460722,"uid":31003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:56:57.000Z","msg":"希望你睇到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一陣見"},{"pid":"85dbe1373259aafc33572927e4df8f4fb8e6cda5","tid":1460722,"uid":31003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gCtbqTU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgCtbqTU.png&h=c573f246&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f6daec535f8206cd4617207a1fd481628cb3edc","tid":1460722,"uid":31003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85dbe1373259aafc33572927e4df8f4fb8e6cda5","tid":1460722,"uid":31003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gCtbqTU.png\" data-thumbnail-